OASISFormat: 0.4
Name:        raygun4ocaml
Version:     0.1.0
Synopsis:    Client for the Raygun error reporting API
Description: Track errors and crashes in real-time 
  in your OCaml programs using the Raygun API.

Authors:     Romain Beauxis
Maintainers: Lidcore <it@lidcore.com>
Homepage:    https://github.com/lidcore/raygun4ocaml
License:     ISC
Plugins:     META (0.4)
BuildTools:  ocamlbuild

Library raygun
  Path:            lib
  Findlibname:     raygun
  Pack:            true
  Modules:         Time, Raygun_t, Stacktrace,
                   Api
  InternalModules: Raygun_j 
  BuildDepends:    ISO8601, atdgen (>= 1.5.0)
  XMETARequires:   ISO8601, atdgen

Flag lwt
  Description: build the Lwt library
  Default$:    false

Library raygun_lwt
  Build$:        flag(lwt)
  Install$:      flag(lwt)
  Path:          lwt
  Findlibname:   lwt
  FindlibParent: raygun
  BuildDepends:  cohttp.lwt, raygun
  XMETARequires: cohttp.lwt, raygun
  Modules:       Raygun_lwt

